# Solution Architecture

## Overview

This project demonstrates a cloud-native Security Information and Event Management (SIEM) architecture using Microsoft Sentinel and Azure monitoring services. Windows Security Events generated by the endpoint are securely collected, stored, analyzed, and investigated within Microsoft Sentinel.

